<section class="sub-section sub-section-mixins">
<h1 class="docs-header">Table Modifiers</h1>
<p>Tabular data can be frustrating to parse if they are not styled properly. BaseWeb provides the mixins and classes you need to make tables and their content a breeze to analyze.</p>

